"! <p class="shorttext synchronized">Object Page Annotations Template</p>
"! Fiori Object Page annotations for ${ENTITY_NAME}
"! @author ${AUTHOR}
"! @date ${DATE}
"! @version 1.0
"!
"! Example usage:
"!   Replace ${ENTITY_NAME} with your projection view name (e.g., ZC_Travel)
"!   Add these annotations to your projection view
